title: MODIS/TERRA MOD17A2 Gross Primary Productivity 8-Day L4 Global 1km
name: modis-terra-mod17a2-gross-primary-productivity-8-day-l4-global-1km
notes: The MODerate-resolution Imaging Spectroradiometer (MODIS) Gross Primary Productivity (GPP) products are a cumulative composite of GPP values based on the radiation use efficiency concept that may be used as inputs to data models for calculating terrestrial energy, carbon, water cycle processes, and biogeochemistry of vegetation. Information on each individual MODIS Platform/Product are available at: https://lpdaac.usgs.gov/lpdaac/products/modis_products_table
